<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP2">
<l>uvanta vuḷḷatta ṉāyula kamaḷan taṇṭamuṟa</l>
<l>nivanta nīṇmuṭi yaṉaṉṟu nērnta nicācararaik</l>
<l>kavarnta veṅkaṇaik kākut taṉkaṭi yārpo ḻilaraṅkat tammāṉaraic</l>
<l>civanta vāṭaiyiṉ mēṟceṉṟa tāmeṉ cintaṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My thoughts went to the red cloth around the waist</l>
<l>of the Lord of Raṅgam, whose groves are filled with scent,</l>
<l>of Kākutstha with scorching arrows</l>
<l rend="indent">that robbed the Rākṣasas who attacked [Him] that day [of their lives],</l>
<l>of Him with the long crown that grew so that it touched the [cosmic] egg,</l>
<l rend="indent">as He measured the world with a rejoicing heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
